features: 🔥 【Easy to Install NG/LPG Gas StoveTop】The 4 burners built-in gas cooktop is easy to install because we provide the pressure regulator in the package, it has a general connection port and you can easily find the right fuel hose. Note:The initial setting of the dual fuel gas cooktop is for natural gas. If you want to use propane, you have to replace the burner nozzle, the conversion kit is in the package.

🔥 【4 High Efficiency Powerful Burners】This 24-inch gas cooktop is equipped with 4 high efficiency sealed burners. The 4 burners include two 5971BTU semi-rapid burners and a 11259BTU rapid burner, one 3412BTU auxiliary burner. These multiple powerful burners can meet your different cooking requirements, such as stewing, frying, baking, steaming and boiling.

🔥 【Thermocouple Protection & 110V Electric Ignition】The gas cooktop 4 burners feature thermocouple flame-out failure divice system(FFD), which will automatically turns off if no flame is detected. Prevent gas leakage, safer. The 24'' stainless steel gas stove top has a 110V AC pulse Ignition system and no battery required.

🔥 【Effortless Cleaning】The 24'' gas stove is made of smooth stainless steel and the stove support bracket on the burner is removable and can be removed for cleaning. It is recommended to clean the 24'' gas hob at least once a week to maintain a healthy and hygienic environment.

🔥 【Built-in Gas Cooktop】The 4 burners gas stove top is built-in design, save more space, perfect for indoor ,apartment use. Drop-in gas cooktop with modern and stylish appearance, looks pleasing to the eye. Stovetop size:23.2 x 20.1 x 4inch Cut-out size:22 x 18.9 inch. Tip:If Amazon does't allow returns, please contact the seller.
